<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 00:37:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>埃及否认以色列声称仍有活跃隧道穿越加沙边境的说法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/egypt-denies-israeli-claims-that-active-tunnels-still-run-across-border-with-gaza/00000191-8ab7-d8c0-abff-9aff5cb20000</link><description>埃及的这一说法不仅与内塔尼亚胡的评估相矛盾，而且与其他以色列高级官员对哈马斯在走廊活动的评估相矛盾</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 00:16:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/egypt-denies-israeli-claims-that-active-tunnels-still-run-across-border-with-gaza/00000191-8ab7-d8c0-abff-9aff5cb20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军命名在加沙中部战斗中丧生的以色列预备役士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-israeli-reserve-soldier-killed-in-central-gaza-combat/00000191-8b95-dd8c-addd-bbf556c40000</link><description>一名预备役军人也在导致来自阿什杜德的 36 岁军士长（预备役）什洛莫·叶霍纳坦·哈祖特 (Shlomo Yehonatan Hazut) 死亡的事件中受重伤。周日上午，以色列国防军宣布，来自杰瓦宾亚米的 21 岁中士戴维·摩西·本·希特里特 (David Moshe Ben Shitrit) 在真主党袭击以色列北部期间身亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 22:29:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-israeli-reserve-soldier-killed-in-central-gaza-combat/00000191-8b95-dd8c-addd-bbf556c40000</guid></item><item><title>今天以色列最重要的新闻与真主党无关</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-25/ty-article/.highlight/the-most-important-news-in-israel-today-had-nothing-to-do-with-hezbollah/00000191-89d8-dc4a-a59b-bbf86add0000</link><description>当我们在多个战线上与外部敌人作战时，以色列仍然因围绕国家民主基础的内部斗争而四分五裂，而这些基础正受到我们自己政府的攻击</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 19:49:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-25/ty-article/.highlight/the-most-important-news-in-israel-today-had-nothing-to-do-with-hezbollah/00000191-89d8-dc4a-a59b-bbf86add0000</guid></item><item><title>“他们只保卫特拉维夫”：以色列北方人在真主党袭击后感到愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/they-only-defend-tel-aviv-israeli-northerners-are-furious-after-hezbollah-attack/00000191-89e5-d31d-a3bf-8fff2c870000</link><description>在以色列先发制人的袭击和真主党对北部的火箭袭击之后，居民感到被遗弃和歧视。以色列北部三名议会主席宣布与政府断绝关系</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 19:33:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/they-only-defend-tel-aviv-israeli-northerners-are-furious-after-hezbollah-attack/00000191-89e5-d31d-a3bf-8fff2c870000</guid></item><item><title>《纽约时报》报道揭示了以色列对哈马斯辛瓦尔“复杂且令人沮丧”的追捕行动的新细节</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/nyt-report-reveals-new-details-of-israels-complex-frustrating-pursuit-of-hamas-sinwar/00000191-8a2f-d13a-ab93-dabfd2c10000</link><description>《纽约时报》报道称，将辛瓦尔与奥萨马·本·拉登进行比较，寻找这位哈马斯领导人“更加复杂，甚至更加令人沮丧”，因为他继续领导哈马斯与以色列进行军事行动</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 18:40:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/nyt-report-reveals-new-details-of-israels-complex-frustrating-pursuit-of-hamas-sinwar/00000191-8a2f-d13a-ab93-dabfd2c10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列水手在真主党袭击以色列北部时丧生；以色列国防军探测船被击中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/israeli-sailor-killed-in-hezbollah-attack-on-northern-israel-idf-probing-ship-hit/00000191-8a4e-d13a-ab93-daff66d80000</link><description>陆军正在调查中士大卫·莫什·本·希特里特是否是被误击其船只的拦截火箭炸死，或者真主党无人机在该船上空被拦截后被弹片炸死</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 18:15:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/israeli-sailor-killed-in-hezbollah-attack-on-northern-israel-idf-probing-ship-hit/00000191-8a4e-d13a-ab93-daff66d80000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯媒体斥责真主党“鸡”袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/arab-media-raps-hezbollah-for-attack-that-didnt-spare-chickens/00000191-8a59-dc4a-a59b-baf91e4a0000</link><description>一位评论员谈到真主党对以色列上个月杀害一名真主党指挥官的反应时表示，“烈士们在目睹复仇的开始时感到高兴”，而真主党的反应只造成了轻微的损害。其他人则指出该组织期待已久的报复行动令人扫兴</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 18:14:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/arab-media-raps-hezbollah-for-attack-that-didnt-spare-chickens/00000191-8a59-dc4a-a59b-baf91e4a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 324 天：纳斯鲁拉称推迟袭击是为了给加沙谈判一个机会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-324-nasrallah-says-attack-was-delayed-to-give-gaza-talks-a-chance/00000191-8a63-d954-add7-8efbd1850001</link><description>以色列国防军表示，在发现真主党准备向以色列北部和中部发射数千枚火箭弹和无人机后，它出动了 100 多架战斗机对真主党发动先发制人的打击。 ■ 真主党领导人纳斯鲁拉表示，伊朗和也门胡塞武装接下来将做出回应 ■ 以色列情报酋长们在停战谈判峰会前抵达开罗 ■ 战争开始 324 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 16:43:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-324-nasrallah-says-attack-was-delayed-to-give-gaza-talks-a-chance/00000191-8a63-d954-add7-8efbd1850001</guid></item><item><title>以色列对黎巴嫩的先发制人打击使其陷入同样的​​战略泥沼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/israels-pre-emptive-strike-in-lebanon-leaves-it-sinking-in-the-same-strategic-mud/00000191-89d5-dc4a-a59b-bbfd9d350000</link><description>挫败真主党从北方发起的进攻是以色列的一项战术成就，但之前的每一次地区升级都是通过外交而不是武力结束的。这次不会有什么不同</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 16:16:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/israels-pre-emptive-strike-in-lebanon-leaves-it-sinking-in-the-same-strategic-mud/00000191-89d5-dc4a-a59b-bbfd9d350000</guid></item><item><title>“他带来了犹太复国主义和犹太议程”：政府批准本格维尔的以色列警察局长人选</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/he-brings-a-zionist-and-jewish-agenda-govt-approves-ben-gvirs-police-chief-pick/00000191-89ee-d13a-ab93-d9ffed110000</link><description>即将上任的警察局长与极右翼国家安全部长关系密切，在担任沿海区指挥官的短暂任期内，犯罪和谋杀案不断上升，并领导了对反政府和反战抗议者的严厉镇压</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 15:55:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/he-brings-a-zionist-and-jewish-agenda-govt-approves-ben-gvirs-police-chief-pick/00000191-89ee-d13a-ab93-d9ffed110000</guid></item><item><title>由于黎巴嫩局势紧张，航空公司取消了以色列航线；英国航空暂停航班至周三</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/airlines-cancel-israel-routes-amid-flare-up-british-airways-halts-flights-until-wednesday/00000191-8992-d954-add7-8fda943c0000</link><description>法航、阿提哈德航空和爱琴海航空虽然取消了其他航班，但仍继续飞往以色列，现已停止所有周日航班</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 15:08:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/airlines-cancel-israel-routes-amid-flare-up-british-airways-halts-flights-until-wednesday/00000191-8992-d954-add7-8fda943c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列联盟和反对派议员敦促对真主党采取更严厉的行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-coalition-opposition-mks-urge-harsher-action-against-hezbollah-as-tensions-soar/00000191-89aa-dc67-ad97-bbfa44710000</link><description>利库德集团议员塔利·戈特利夫（Tally Gotliv）无视该党关于以色列-真主党袭击的采访禁令，呼吁“对真主党进行无情的攻击”右翼反对派议会成员也敦促以色列“结束克制”</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 14:46:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-coalition-opposition-mks-urge-harsher-action-against-hezbollah-as-tensions-soar/00000191-89aa-dc67-ad97-bbfa44710000</guid></item><item><title>袭击受挫后，以色列和真主党恢复战时“正常”状态</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/after-thwarted-attack-its-back-to-wartime-normal-for-israel-and-hezbollah/00000191-8952-dc4a-a59b-bbfa2cd10000</link><description>当真主党试图攻击北部的军事基地和以色列中部的安全设施时，它扩大了限制。但哈马斯领导人全面战争的梦想仍然遥不可及，真主党可能正在寻求平息战火</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 12:35:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/after-thwarted-attack-its-back-to-wartime-normal-for-israel-and-hezbollah/00000191-8952-dc4a-a59b-bbfa2cd10000</guid></item><item><title>即使在与被释放的人质交谈时，内塔尼亚胡也只关注自己的痛苦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/even-when-talking-to-ex-hostages-the-netanyahus-focus-on-their-own-pain/00000191-890a-d847-abff-ebabd4b90000</link><description>与此同时，艾萨克·赫尔佐格总统应该放弃米里·雷格夫 (Miri Regev) 在 10 月 7 日一年后举行纪念加沙边境社区仪式的计划</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 12:03:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/even-when-talking-to-ex-hostages-the-netanyahus-focus-on-their-own-pain/00000191-890a-d847-abff-ebabd4b90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对真主党的先发制人打击是如何展开的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article-timeline/.premium/how-israels-preemptive-strike-against-hezbollah-unfolded/00000191-88cc-d632-add9-b9ff77480000</link><description>自上个月末高级指挥官福阿德·舒克尔被定点杀害以来，以色列一直准备迎接真主党的报复 ■ 周日早些时候，以色列国防军对真主党声称的第一阶段反应进行了先发制人的打击 ■ 以色列后方司令部宣布了新的指导方针对于中午 12:30 被驱逐的居民 ■ 真主党领导人纳斯鲁拉将于下午 6 点发表讲话</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 11:17:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article-timeline/.premium/how-israels-preemptive-strike-against-hezbollah-unfolded/00000191-88cc-d632-add9-b9ff77480000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡告诉被释放的加沙人质，他在以色列军队期间“在囚禁训练中遭到殴打”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/netanyahu-tells-released-hostages-he-was-beaten-in-captivity-training-while-in-idf/00000191-88bc-d460-abd3-f8be6bb90000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡发表此番言论之前，一名被释放的人质作了证词，她告诉内塔尼亚胡她在加沙被关押期间如何遭到殴打和酷刑，而她的一位亲戚也出席了会议，询问总理：“以色列是否明白，在那里被强奸的年轻女性？</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 11:13:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/netanyahu-tells-released-hostages-he-was-beaten-in-captivity-training-while-in-idf/00000191-88bc-d460-abd3-f8be6bb90000</guid></item><item><title>Ben-Gvir 在以色列报纸上刊登广告，指责 Shin Bet 首席执行官“10 月 7 日失败”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-runs-ad-against-shin-bet-chief-for-failing-on-october-7-in-israeli-newspapers/00000191-888c-d460-abd3-f88e74460000</link><description>该广告包括 Ben-Gvir 的 Otzma Yehudit 政党的标志和 Shin Bet 首席执行官 Ronen Bar 的照片，声称 Bar“在 10 月 7 日失败，正在导致以色列陷入另一场灾难”，并补充说“对鲁莽的交易说不”。首相办公室尚未回应</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 09:27:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-runs-ad-against-shin-bet-chief-for-failing-on-october-7-in-israeli-newspapers/00000191-888c-d460-abd3-f88e74460000</guid></item><item><title>从庇护所到聚会，这些是以色列公众在真主党威胁下的指导方针</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/from-shelters-to-gatherings-the-guidelines-for-the-israeli-public-amid-hezbollah-threat/00000191-88c5-dd90-a7d1-cbffc5970000</link><description>以色列后方司令部宣布了针对 30 个地区中 14 个地区居民的新准则，其中包括大特拉维夫地区、整个加利利地区和大海法地区</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 09:17:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/from-shelters-to-gatherings-the-guidelines-for-the-israeli-public-amid-hezbollah-threat/00000191-88c5-dd90-a7d1-cbffc5970000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙地带南部被爆炸装置炸死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-by-explosive-device-in-southern-gaza-strip/00000191-8868-d1a4-abbf-896ed2670000</link><description>据以色列国防军称，阿米特·萨迪科夫上士的死亡是自10月7日战争爆发以来第700名士兵死亡，也是自几周后以色列军队进入加沙以来第367名士兵阵亡。</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 08:31:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-by-explosive-device-in-southern-gaza-strip/00000191-8868-d1a4-abbf-896ed2670000</guid></item><item><title>尽管真主党升级，以色列代表团仍将前往开罗参加加沙协议谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/despite-hezbollah-escalation-israeli-delegation-to-leave-for-gaza-deal-talks-in-cairo/00000191-8836-d460-abd3-f8362f460000</link><description>尽管人们越来越怀疑其是否有能力取得突破，但仍决定派遣代表团参加开罗峰会，这可能表明以色列认为周日黎巴嫩边境的暴力升级已经结束</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 07:16:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-25/ty-article/.premium/despite-hezbollah-escalation-israeli-delegation-to-leave-for-gaza-deal-talks-in-cairo/00000191-8836-d460-abd3-f8362f460000</guid></item></channel></rss>